---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { site } from "../config";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="py-8 md:py-12">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl dark:text-slate-100"
    >
      About
    </h1>
    <div
      class="mt-8 max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
    >
      <p>
        Hi — I'm {site.name}. I've spent over 20 years in software, after
        six years in the U.S. Navy, and along the way I've grown from
        engineer to engineering leader. Today I'm Director of Engineering
        at <a
          href="https://www.patriotsoftware.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-indigo-600 underline-offset-4 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400"
          >Patriot Software</a
        >, where I've been for almost 5 years leading a nationally
        distributed organization of 60+ engineers and QA professionals
        building SaaS HR, Payroll, Time, and Accounting platforms.
      </p>
      <p>
        The work I find most rewarding is the intersection of three things:
        developing strong engineering leaders, modernizing platforms onto
        cloud-native architectures, and embedding AI deeply into the SDLC
        so teams can ship more, faster, and with less toil. Earlier in my
        career I led teams at Oracle, Liberty Mutual, Bose, and Mutual
        Benefit Group, with consulting stops in between, and I started out
        building FAA weather systems at Harris Corporation. I hold a B.S.
        in Computer Science from the University of Central Florida.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work, life is centered on family and the outdoors. I
        live in Harrisburg, PA with my wife Geneva — we've been married
        for 36 years. We have two grown kids and three grandkids who, I'm
        very lucky to say, live close enough that we get to spend a lot of
        time together. They're honestly my favorite people. When Geneva
        and I get a free weekend, you'll usually find us out camping or on
        a trail somewhere.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm also genuinely a tech and learning addict — most of my
        non-family free time goes into side projects and digging into
        whatever the AI world is doing this month. This site is the home
        for some of those projects (running on subdomains) and a place to
        share a bit about who I am. Take a look at the{" "}
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="text-indigo-600 underline-offset-4 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400"
          >projects page</a
        >, browse my{" "}
        <a
          href="/resume"
          class="text-indigo-600 underline-offset-4 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400"
          >resume</a
        >, or drop me a note via the{" "}
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="text-indigo-600 underline-offset-4 hover:underline dark:text-indigo-400"
          >contact page</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div
        class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 dark:border-slate-800"
      >
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-slate-500 uppercase dark:text-slate-400">
          What I focus on
        </h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <li>Scaling and developing engineering leaders</li>
          <li>Cloud modernization (AWS, Azure, OCI) and microservices</li>
          <li>Embedding AI/LLM tooling into the SDLC</li>
          <li>Agile, CI/CD, and delivery excellence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div
        class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 dark:border-slate-800"
      >
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-slate-500 uppercase dark:text-slate-400">
          Off the clock
        </h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <li>Time with Geneva, our kids, and our grandkids</li>
          <li>Camping and hiking</li>
          <li>Side projects and tinkering with AI tools</li>
          <li>U.S. Navy veteran</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
